We stayed for 5 nights
beautiful little rooms
friendly staff
and a great location
$10 dollar taxis (4 people the price of the subway) takes you to the Village
Central Park
a little farther to Wall St
Walk to Time Sq
and the Theatres in 10 minutes
Have Breakfast at the Red Flame just West toward 6th
Don't let the doorman talk you into a $25 to $35 fixed price Black Cab when the metered Yellow Cabs will go there for $10
Tour with the Blue Line Hop on Hop off Bus
$54 gets you 4 tours over 48 hours: Uppper Manhattan
Lower Manhattan
Night tour
and the boat cruise
all for one price
We 2 couples would definitely go back
